name: Aved Luun (V)
Lore: 'Shaman of her Jawa tribe. Mate of Kalit. Suspects betrayal from her mate''s rival, Wittin.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Adds one battle destiny with Kalit. Your Jawas and sandcrawlers are destiny +2. May deploy Jawa Camp, Sergeant Doallyn, or Thedit on table from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
